Hercules Inc said it namedDavid Hollingsworth as chairman and chief executive, succeedingAlexander Giacco who is retiring effective April 1.    Hercules also said it named Fred Buckner as president andchief operating officer and Arden Engebretsen as vice chairmanand chief financial officer.    The company also said it expects its new product, Synpulp,to grow into a 100 mln dlr a year business over the next fiveyears. Metton, another new product, is expected to yield300-500 mln dlrs a year by the late 1990s. Reuter&#3;